<section class="py-10 md:py-14 bg-white">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="mt-7 space-y-4">
      <details class="rounded-lg ring-1 ring-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.06)] p-4 bg-white">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">Do I need to bring an ID or fill out any forms?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.65)]">
          No. Just show up during the location's posted hours—no documentation needed.
        </p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-lg ring-1 ring-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.06)] p-4 bg-white">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">When and where are the collection sites available?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.65)]">
          Use the <a href="/#finder" class="underline text-[#FF6B35] hover:text-[#C86D4B]">site finder</a> to see nearby locations. Each site sets its own hours—check the card for address, phone, and hours. You can also tap <strong>Near Me</strong> to center the map on your location.
        </p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-lg ring-1 ring-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.06)] p-4 bg-white">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">Can I donate money instead of food?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.65)]">
          Yes! You can purchase food directly through our Amazon registry—items ship to us and we deliver to collection sites. Visit the <a href="/donate" class="underline text-[#FF6B35] hover:text-[#C86D4B]">Donate</a> page to get started.
        </p>
      </details>
      
      <details class="rounded-lg ring-1 ring-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.06)] p-4 bg-white">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">What should I donate?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.65)]">
          Non‑perishable, shelf‑stable items are best (canned foods, pasta, rice, peanut butter, etc.). See our <a href="/#what-to-donate" class="underline text-[#FF6B35] hover:text-[#C86D4B]">What to Donate</a> guide for ideas.
        </p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-lg ring-1 ring-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.06)] p-4 bg-white">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">How can my business or organization get involved?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.65)]">
          We welcome new collection partners! <a href="/become-a-partner" class="underline text-[#FF6B35] hover:text-[#C86D4B]">Register your business or organization here</a> to join as a site.
        </p>
      </details>
      <details class="rounded-lg ring-1 ring-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.06)] p-4 bg-white">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer font-semibold">What if I have more questions?</summary>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:rgb(0_0_0_/_0.65)]">
          Reach out via our <a href="/contact" class="underline text-[#FF6B35] hover:text-[#C86D4B]">contact form</a> and we'll be happy to help!
        </p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


